sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor       User as User
    participant FE    as Frontend<br/>(Next.js)
    participant BE    as Backend<br/>(NestJS)
    participant DB    as Database

    %% ── Phase 1: Create Specialized Community ──────────────────────
    rect rgb(224, 242, 254)
        Note over User,DB: Phase 1 — Create Specialized Community

        User ->>+ FE : Enter Name, Slug, Description, and click "Create Community"
        FE ->>+ BE : POST /api/communities { name, slug, description }
        Note over BE : JwtAuthGuard + EmailVerifiedGuard

        BE ->>+ DB : Query if community slug already exists (prisma.community.findUnique)
        DB -->>- BE : Existing community record or null

        BE ->>+ DB : Create community record with owner membership (prisma.community.create)
        DB -->>- BE : Created community record

        BE -->>- FE : 201 Created — Community JSON
        FE ->> FE : Redirect to /c/[slug]
        FE -->>- User : Render new community dashboard
    end

    %% ── Phase 2: Join / Leave Community ────────────────────────────
    rect rgb(236, 253, 245)
        Note over User,DB: Phase 2 — Join / Leave Community

        User ->>+ FE : Click Join / Leave button
        FE ->>+ BE : POST /api/communities/:id/join
        Note over BE : JwtAuthGuard + BannedUserGuard

        BE ->>+ DB : Query if user is banned (prisma.communityBannedUser.findUnique)
        DB -->>- BE : Banned status or null

        BE ->>+ DB : Query existing membership (prisma.communityMember.findUnique)
        DB -->>- BE : Membership record or null

        BE ->>+ DB : Create membership (join) OR delete membership (leave)
        DB -->>- BE : Mutation success

        BE ->> BE : Invalidate cache (communities graph, user views)
        BE -->>- FE : 200 OK — { joined: boolean }
        FE ->> FE : router.refresh() (server component updates)
        FE -->>- User : Toggle button text (Join/Leave) & update member count
    end

    %% ── Phase 3: Manage Rules & Members (e.g. Add Rule) ───────────
     rect rgb(255, 247, 237)
        Note over User,DB: Phase 3 — Manage Rules & Members (e.g. Add Rule)

        User ->>+ FE : Enter rule title/description, click "Add Rule"
        FE ->>+ BE : POST /api/communities/:id/rules { title, description }
        Note over BE : JwtAuthGuard + BannedUserGuard

        BE ->>+ DB : Check if user is Owner/Mod (prisma.communityMember.findUnique)
        DB -->>- BE : Member record (role: OWNER or MOD)

        BE ->>+ DB : Create rule record (prisma.communityRule.create)
        DB -->>- BE : Created rule record

        BE -->>- FE : 201 Created
        FE ->> FE : router.refresh() (re-fetch rules list)
        FE -->>- User : Show new rule in rules list
    end
